{"tid":1868124,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《PD》造假不是私慾 而是練習生不想出道","createTime":"2020-02-07T11:51:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T12:23:49.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"12dfa92d970ed724f68336588f1b1f5623f27f93","tid":1868124,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:51:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/KoreaStar/M.1581073748.A.2C7.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FKoreaStar%2FM.1581073748.A.2C7.html&d=%2FXNhycaKVB9NPWqbniWxn4m5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=0cca6295\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/KoreaStar/M.1581073748.A.2C7.html</a><br />\n韓國時間7日下午2時首爾中央地方法院對《Produce》系列造假事件相關安PD-金PD等進行了首次公審。對於受到企劃社款待，為了利益進行排名造假的說法，安俊英PD方面表示，金勇範-安俊英PD在直播放送前一天直接或間接地聽說特定練習生不想進入出道組，因此接受了退出的意願。所以相關練習生排名下降。其他練習生進入出道組。這並不是因為個人私慾或不正當請求。李某PD只是按照上級的決定去做的。"},{"pid":"0fb2f3d36042adc2408deb8b759b7da4a18f5876","tid":1868124,"uid":104502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:52:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd080447db8d3cf35cb01bd506461364d172981b","tid":1868124,"uid":229026,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:52:40.000Z","msg":"佢講出嚟會唔會都覺得離譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e65ab3fd67a4f0b1b7d9693df006c0652a986728","tid":1868124,"uid":189235,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"cd080447db8d3cf35cb01bd506461364d172981b","tid":1868124,"uid":229026,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:52:40.000Z","msg":"佢講出嚟會唔會都覺得離譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:54:07.000Z","msg":"應該